 <br>
This sound like a cool ability.  I don't have much fun as a tank in RvR, so my BM could benefit from a PvE RA to help guildies out.  Hoever, the Aug CON 3 pre-req is absurd.  Could you ask about making this a stand-alone RA?  I can't imagine this would unbalancing - I can't actually believe anyone has this RA on live servers today!<br>
<br>
Also, why are there three levels of this?  Progressively larger areas?  I'm assuming the taunt effect here is absolute, and that this RA will even get aggro away fromt he healer who just used a group insta - if not, this RA shuld carry a warning label.  :)<br>
